|:-----------------------------------|:------------------------------------------------------------------|:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| <span class='smallcaps'>1</span>   | [Morpheme wire-1pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:wire-1pro) |                                                                                       |
| <span class='smallcaps'>1+2</span> |                                                                   | [Morpheme ejne-1-2pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:ejne-1-2pro)                 |
| <span class='smallcaps'>1+3</span> |                                                                   | [Morpheme ana-1-3pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:ana-1-3pro)                   |
| <span class='smallcaps'>2</span>   | [Morpheme mere-2pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:mere-2pro) | [Morpheme monkontomo-2pl-pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:monkontomo-2pl-pro)   |
| <span class='smallcaps'>3</span>   | [Morpheme tewi-3pro](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:tewi-3pro) | [Morpheme tewisantomo-3pro-pl](MorphsetTable?no_translation#cldf:tewisantomo-3pro-pl) |

